---
import EventLayout from "../../components/EventLayout.astro";

const images = [
  { src: "/get-sip-done/1.png", alt: "Get Sip Done Antwerp" },
];
---

<EventLayout
  title="Get Sip Done: Antwerp Kick-Off"
  date="November 28, 2025"
  location="The Beacon, Antwerp"
  type="Breakfast"
  description="A founder breakfast at The Beacon connecting Antwerp builders, operators, and investors over coffee and conversation."
  images={images}
>
  <p>Not every connection needs a hackathon or a stage. Sometimes it just takes coffee and the right people in the same room at the right time.</p>
  <p>Get Sip Done brought founders, operators, and investors together at The Beacon for a morning of unstructured conversation. No pitches, no panels - just builders meeting builders over breakfast.</p>
</EventLayout>
